{"tid":1969844,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"諸事不順皆因不孝，諸事不順皆因犯邪淫","createTime":"2020-04-12T17:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T01:31:34.000Z","uid":35484,"like":8,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5501dda7ff699c40b48ff864c1dc83cdd411f24d","tid":1969844,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:00:31.000Z","msg":"純推ＰＯＳＴ，唔洗睇回覆，有問題請到ＴＧ群發問<br />\n戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zojx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=7bfef923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n諸事不順皆因不孝，諸事不順皆因犯邪淫<br />\n<br />\n只要犯以上兩種，你既運氣，人生，福報就會不斷下降，這是千真萬確既事實<br />\n想要人生變得更好，第一孝順，第二戒邪淫，（包括打丁，叫雞，一夜情等等），第三行善積德<br />\n只要照住上面３樣去做好一年，你會慢慢發覺自己既人生越黎越好。<br />\n<br />\n可睇秦東魁老師講既ＹＯＵＴＵＢＥ視頻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zojx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=37273a9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA</a><br />\n<br />\n邪淫的25種果報１，２，３，之後可以順住睇落去<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLyVAEphpUDM&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zojx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=19e8d962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c8W7F3saOyI&amp;t=2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc8W7F3saOyI%26t%3D2s&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zojx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=a4cd3aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c8W7F3saOyI&amp;t=2s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EJ2S8TLBXqk&amp;t=527s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEJ2S8TLBXqk%26t%3D527s&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zojx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=44c4d968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EJ2S8TLBXqk&amp;t=527s</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎"},{"pid":"b64b41cdc9755fa7e6fa0c1648a58904d8660944","tid":1969844,"uid":244845,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母on9仔"},{"pid":"06219ed4cdc660fb46e0b6d9da13f7f357541711","tid":1969844,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T18:00:04.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"557153151f33c10192c72c23c15ac6bbeff0b45e","tid":1969844,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac3284e58237e94b7c051b46bc9b583482ddb69","tid":1969844,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcd93ec053fb284d48ccc701c3e1d891e224e83","tid":1969844,"uid":355887,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"Ching 我明白你的好意 我決定再打一發先訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e33cd54545a9b41c4ce6f34381601b2ea72bac","tid":1969844,"uid":36097,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bfcd93ec053fb284d48ccc701c3e1d891e224e83","tid":1969844,"uid":355887,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"Ching 我明白你的好意 我決定再打一發先訓<img src=\"/as